flowchart TD

A[Game Start] --> B[Load Level Grid]
B --> C[Spawn Pac-Man]
C --> D[Spawn Ghosts]
D --> E[Enter GameState: Playing]

E --> GAMELOOP[Game Loop]

GAMELOOP --> PAUSE{Pause Input?}
PAUSE -- Yes --> PAUSED[GameState: Paused]
PAUSED --> MENU{User Choice}
MENU -- Resume --> GAMELOOP
MENU -- Restart --> A
MENU -- Quit --> EXIT[Exit Game]

PAUSE -- No --> VICTORY{All Pellets Eaten?}
VICTORY -- Yes --> NEXTLVL[Load Next Level]
NEXTLVL --> B

VICTORY -- No --> UPDATE[Update Entities]
UPDATE --> PACMOVE[Pac-Man Moves]
PACMOVE --> GHOSTMOVE[Ghosts Move via AI]
GHOSTMOVE --> COLLISIONS[Check Collisions]

COLLISIONS --> PACCOL{Pac-Man Collision?}

PACCOL -- Pellet --> PELTYPE{Pellet Type?}
PELTYPE -- Normal Pellet --> ADDPTS[Add Points]
ADDPTS --> DESTROY1[Destroy Pellet]
DESTROY1 --> GAMELOOP

PELTYPE -- Power Pellet --> BIGPTS[Add Bonus Points]
BIGPTS --> FRIGHTEN[Ghosts Enter Frightened Mode]
FRIGHTEN --> DESTROY2[Destroy Power Pellet]
DESTROY2 --> GAMELOOP

PACCOL -- Ghost --> GHOSTSTATE{Ghost State?}
GHOSTSTATE -- Frightened --> EATGHOST[Eat Ghost]
EATGHOST --> GHOSTPTS[Add Ghost Points]
GHOSTPTS --> RESPAWNGHOST[Ghost Returns to House]
RESPAWNGHOST --> GAMELOOP

GHOSTSTATE -- Normal/Chase/Scatter --> PACDIE[Pac-Man Dies]
PACDIE --> DECLIVES[Decrease Lives]
DECLIVES --> CHECKLIVES{Lives > 0?}
CHECKLIVES -- Yes --> RESPAWN[Respawn Pac-Man & Reset Ghosts]
RESPAWN --> GAMELOOP
CHECKLIVES -- No --> GAMEOVER[Game Over]

PACCOL -- No Collision --> GAMELOOP
